"you can tweak your object such that you can revert the direction of the "
"screw operation (by reverting the angular vector of the height), meaning "
"you can revert the clockwise and counterclockwise direction of some "
"operations, and also adjust the angular vectors of the profile, bending "
"it accordingly. (See Fig. :ref:`fig-mesh-screw-interactive-panel`.)"
